OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FAnjem Choudary was told he risked
OL,8,Fcausing the deaths of "very many
OL,9,Fpeople" as he was jailed for life with
OL,10,Fa minimum term of 28 years for running
OL,11,Fa banned terrorist organisation.
OL,13,FThe 57-year-old, of Ilford, east
OL,14,FLondon, was convicted last week of
OL,15,Ftaking a caretaker role in directing
OL,16,FAl-Muhajiroun (ALM) while its founder
OL,17,Fwas in jail.
