OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FHe was also found guilty of
OL,8,Fencouraging support for it through
OL,9,Fonline lectures to the Islamic
OL,10,FThinkers Society (ITS), which
OL,11,Fprosecutors said was another name for
OL,12,FALM.
OL,14,FSentencing him at Woolwich Crown Court
OL,15,Fon Tuesday, Mr Justice Mark Wall told
OL,16,F"dangerous" Choudary, who stood in the
OL,17,Fdock motionless wearing a white t-
OL,18,Fshirt, that he will not be liable for
OL,19,Fparole until he is 85 years old.
