OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FThe judge said: "Taken together, your
OL,8,Factions while directing Al-Muhajiroun
OL,9,Fran the risk of causing or
OL,10,Fcontributing to the deaths of very
OL,11,Fmany people.
OL,13,F"In addition, by running an
OL,14,Forganisation such as Al-Muhajiroun,
OL,15,Fyou contributed in a significant way
OL,16,Fto the fear of terrorist attack by
OL,17,Fradical Islamic organisations which
OL,18,Fthen existed in this country and
OL,19,Fabroad.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/17
