OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,F"You also helped to undermine the
OL,8,Fattempts of many good people to foster
OL,9,Fbonds between Muslims and people of
OL,10,Fother faiths and none who then lived
OL,11,Fin the United Kingdom."
OL,13,FMr Justice Wall described Choudary as
OL,14,Fan "intelligent man and a persuasive
OL,15,Fspeaker" to those open to "messages of
OL,16,Fhate", saying he possesses "great
OL,17,Fdetermination" in pursing his aims.
