OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FHe went on: "You have no doubt as to
OL,8,Fthe rectitude of your views. Your
OL,9,Fviews are entrenched and abhorrent to
OL,10,Fmost right-thinking people."
OL,12,FThe judge told of "chilling" trial
OL,13,Fevidence about Choudary's denial of
OL,14,Fthe holocaust and jokes about the 9/11
OL,15,Fterror attacks.
