OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FHe added: "I do not sentence you for
OL,8,Fholding those views, but the fact that
OL,9,Fyou genuinely hold such extreme views
OL,10,Fcoupled with your history of unlawful
OL,11,Fbehaviour is an indication of the
OL,12,Fdanger you pose into the future.
OL,14,F"I am sure that you will continue to
OL,15,Fpreach your message of hate and
OL,16,Fdivision when or if you are given the
OL,17,Fopportunity to do so in the future.
OL,19,F"You are not someone who can be
OL,20,Fdiverted from that course by any form
OL,21,Fof intervention.
