OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,F"You pose a significant risk of
OL,8,Fcausing serious harm to members of the
OL,9,Fpublic into the future by committing
OL,10,Ffurther specified offences such as
OL,11,Fthis."
OL,13,FThe judge also told the Islamist
OL,14,Fpreacher that organisations such as
OL,15,FALM "normalise violence in the pursuit
OL,16,Fof an ideological cause", giving
OL,17,Fmembers "the courage to commit acts
OL,18,Fthat otherwise they might not do".
