OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FHe went on: "They drive a wedge
OL,8,Fbetween people who would and could
OL,9,Flive together in peaceful co-
OL,10,Fexistence."
OL,12,FChoudary was "front and centre" in
OL,13,Frunning ALM, the judge said, and he
OL,14,F"sought to groom" young people into
OL,15,Fhis way of thinking.
