OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FMr Justice Wall added: "I do not
OL,8,Fconclude that you only targeted young
OL,9,Fpeople but you were prepared to
OL,10,Fencourage young men into radical
OL,11,Factivity and did so when you must have
OL,12,Fknown that the appropriate course was
OL,13,Fto refuse to indoctrinate people of
OL,14,Ftheir ages."
OL,16,FDuring the hearing, defence barrister
OL,17,FPaul Hynes KC said that by the time
OL,18,FChoudary had started directing ALM, it
OL,19,Fwas "little more than a husk of an
OL,20,Forganisation" and he was not
OL,21,F"gathering the masses to join".
