OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FIt came after an investigation by the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police, the New York
OL,9,FPolice Department (NYPD) and the Royal
OL,10,FCanadian Mounted Police.
OL,12,FITS was infiltrated by undercover law
OL,13,Fenforcement officers in the US, who
OL,14,Fwere present at online lectures in
OL,15,F2022 and 2023, held over the Element
OL,16,Fmessenger platform.
OL,18,FALM was proscribed as a terror
OL,19,Forganisation in the UK in 2010, though
OL,20,Fit was said in court the group has
OL,21,Fcontinued to exist under various names.
