OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FA senior security official said last
OL,8,Fweek's conviction was a "significant
OL,9,Fmoment", adding the evidence presented
OL,10,Fin court showed "Choudary's continued
OL,11,Finvolvement in supporting terrorism
OL,12,Fand radicalising others".
OL,14,FCommander Dominic Murphy, head of the
OL,15,FMetropolitan Police's counter-
OL,16,Fterrorism command, said: "There are
OL,17,Findividuals that have conducted
OL,18,Fterrorist attacks or travelled for
OL,19,Fterrorist purposes as a result of
OL,20,FAnjem Choudary's radicalising impact
OL,21,Fupon them."
