OL,7,FNYPD deputy commissioner Rebecca
OL,8,FWeiner said it was a "historic case",
OL,9,Fdescribing Choudary as a "shameless,
OL,10,Fprolific radicaliser".
OL,12,FMs Weiner said: "It is usually the
OL,13,Ffoot soldiers, the individuals, who
OL,14,Fare brought into the network who go on
OL,15,Fto commit the attacks who are brought
OL,16,Fto justice.
OL,18,F"And it's rarely the leader, which is
OL,19,Fwhat makes this a particularly
OL,20,Fimportant moment."
