OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FProsecutor Tom Little KC, opening the
OL,8,Ftrial at Woolwich Crown Court on June
OL,9,F13, said Choudary had a "warped and
OL,10,Ftwisted mindset".
OL,12,FOmar Bakri Muhammad, who founded ALM,
OL,13,Fwas in prison in Lebanon between 2014
OL,14,Fand March 2023, and Choudary stepped
OL,15,Fin and "filled the void", Mr Little
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,FIn 2016, Choudary was convicted and
OL,19,Fjailed for five-and-a-half years for
OL,20,Fsupporting the so-called Islamic State.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/17
