OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,FThe judge told him: "I am sure that
OL,8,Fyou were in awe of Anjem Choudary and
OL,9,Fbecame involved in this offence partly
OL,10,Fbecause of his influence over you.
OL,12,F"However, I am equally sure that you
OL,13,Fknew full well what you were getting
OL,14,Finvolved in and were anxious to become
OL,15,Fever more deeply involved in it.
OL,17,F"I have regard to the fact that the
OL,18,Forganisation of which you became a
OL,19,Fpart was not proscribed in Canada,
OL,20,Fwhere you lived.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/17
