OL,3,CAnjem Choudary 'ran risk of causing
OL,4,Cdeaths of many people' by directing
OL,5,Cterror
OL,7,F"However, it is clear from the
OL,8,Fevidence at trial that you were aware
OL,9,Fof the nature of the organisation of
OL,10,Fwhich you became a part and its status
OL,11,Fin the United Kingdom which made it
OL,12,Fdifficult for those such as Anjem
OL,13,FChoudary to participate openly in its
OL,14,Factivities."
OL,16,FEvidence showed how Hussein was
OL,17,Feffectively acting as a personal
OL,18,Fassistant to Choudary, helping to host
OL,19,Fonline lectures and editing extremist
OL,20,Fonline blogs and publications for him.
