OL,7,FDefence barrister Hossein Zahir KC
OL,8,Fargued Hussein was a "wholly inactive"
OL,9,Fmember.
OL,11,FChoudary was arrested in east London
OL,12,Fon July 17 last year while Hussein,
OL,13,Ffrom Edmonton, was detained at
OL,14,FHeathrow Airport, having arrived on a
OL,15,Fflight the same day.
OL,17,FScotland Yard said Hussein had planned
OL,18,Fto visit Choudary.
